<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  {{ template "head.gtml" "about" }}
  <body>
    <main>
      <h1 id="faq">FAQ</h1>
      <p id="highl">Just another pomf.se clone...</p>
      <ul>
    	<li>Maximum upload file size is 32MiB. All uploads are public.</li>
    	<li>Currently all content is allowed under German law. Malware and 
                child porn is not welcome here.</li>
    	<li>All filetypes are allowed, except exe, bat, cmd, msi or similar 
                (Due to malware).</li>
    	<li>No logs are kept, no logs over uploading nor over downloading.</li>
    	<li>We're non-profit and offer this service for free without ads.</li>
    	<li>For removal of a file or to submit abuse reports (DMCA) see our 
                contact section.</li>
        <li>All files were uploaded by anonymous users. The operators are not 
                responsible for any files hosted on this site.</li>
    	<li>URLs can be shortend by replacing <code>https://regist.ra.rs</code>
                with <code>https://s.te.rs</code>.</li>
      </ul>

      <h1 id="stats">Stats</h1>
      <p>Currently serving {{ .N }} files, making up ~{{ .S }} MB.</p>

      <h1 name="contact">Contact</h1>
      <p>To report abuse (Notice and Take-Down, etc) or any other 
      matter, contact me <a href="mailto:xatasan@firemail.cc">via email</a>
      or <a href="https://twitter.com/xatasan">via twitter</a>. 
      Twitter will also be used for general updates.</p>

      {{ template "nav.gtml" }}
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
